
1. Set AllowOverride to All for root folder

# vim /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf
<Directory "/var/www/html">
.........
AllowOverride All
</Directory>



2. Change owner of api to apache.apache for logs to be able to be written to /var/www/html/apiv1/logs/

# umask 022
# chown -R root.root /var/www/html/apiv1/
# chown -R apache.apache /var/www/html/apiv1/logs

Install composer:
# cd /var/www/html/apiv1/
# vim composer.json:
{
    "require": {
        "slim/slim": "2.*",
        "monolog/monolog": "1.19"
    }
}
# rm -f composer.lock
# composer install

3. Change mysql password in php scripts

# egrep -Hira PASSWORD_HERE *
4. Test API

# curl http://127.0.0.1/apiv1/

{
    "error": false,
    "message": "API",
    "status": "200"
}



